title: Portable Adobe Photoshop CS4 En-Fr-De-It-Es
description:
Portable Photoshop CS4 En-Fr-De-It-Es


Graphic editor without installation.

Extract (with a PortableApps folder at the device's root) and run PhotoshopPortable.
If you downloaded previsous version, replace launcher to fix erasing Quick Launch, Address Book... in AppDataMicrosoft.
Thanks to vanbasten for italian and dubre for german. 
Included optional plug-ins and presets(thanks to Anne-Marie).
If you drag'n drop a file on (or open with) PhotoshopPortable: it will be opened in Photoshop.
Settings of installed Photoshop should be preserved but not sure for registration.
Many keys left in HKCRCLSID if you don't want it: don't use...
